{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ENGAGE IN SPECTACULAR NAVAL COMBAT </h2>Prepare for devastating battles by crafting a dozen different ships and equip your fleet with powerful loadouts. Unlock stronger weapons as you progress and customize your ships to reflect your unique pirate playstyle.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/GIF_SAB_01.gif?t=1736523191\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SAIL INTO A DANGEROUS HELL IN PARADISE</h2>Voyage into the Indian Ocean and explore a vast open world teeming with cutthroat pirates, deadly sea monsters, supernatural threats, devastating storms, and more.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/GIF_SAB_02.gif?t=1736523191\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TEAM UP WITH FELLOW PIRATES</h2>Sail the lawless seas solo or team up with two friends or other players to partake in shareable contracts and rewards.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/GIF_SAB_03.gif?t=1736523191\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ENJOY EVER-EVOLVING CONTENT</h2>Each season, face a brand-new legendary sea lord and discover fresh content, limitless endgame opportunities, and new exciting features designed to enhance your pirate experience.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2853730/extras/GIF_SAB_04.gif?t=1736523191\" /><br><br>Persistent internet connection and Ubisoft account required.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hello, World!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2853730/1b3c481dec1208df052ff8054af6ae8f5f2f0eb9.jpg"},{"name":"Home of Compagnie Royale","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2853730/3ad3d8e33a0e8d6da05e5944851332302b10d345.jpg"},{"name":"It's More Fun Together!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.ste